<description>TORNADO WATCH 23 REMAINS VALID UNTIL 10 PM EST THIS EVENING FOR
THE FOLLOWING AREAS
IN NORTH CAROLINA THIS WATCH INCLUDES 4 COUNTIES
IN PIEDMONT NORTH CAROLINA
CABARRUS              MECKLENBURG           ROWAN
UNION NC
IN SOUTH CAROLINA THIS WATCH INCLUDES 2 COUNTIES
IN UPSTATE SOUTH CAROLINA
CHESTER               YORK
THIS INCLUDES THE CITIES OF BLACKSTOCK, CATAWBA, CHARLOTTE,
CHESTER, CONCORD, CORNWELL, GREAT FALLS, HUNTERSVILLE,
INDIAN TRAIL, KANNAPOLIS, MATTHEWS, MONROE, ROCK HILL, SALISBURY,
TRINITY, AND WEDDINGTON.</description>
